room_title: Escape room "Budapest Express" by Escapology St. Peters in St. Louis
room_address: 4105 N. Cloverleaf Dr. Suite B St. Peters, MO 63376
room_description: Central Europe, February 25th 1931.On your way to a detective conference with your closest colleagues, you're traveling onboard the famous Budapest Express. Suddenly a knock on the door interrupts your peaceful journey. The manager needs your help: a first-class passenger has been murdered. It had to have been one of the passengers! You have to figure it before you become the next victim!
